statements: SELECT * FROM diet_impact_fitness_goals WHERE age > 30;
SELECT username, age, weight FROM diet_impact_fitness_goals WHERE gender = 'Female' AND diet_type = 'Keto';
SELECT user_id, diet_type, fitness_goal FROM diet_impact_fitness_goals ORDER BY fitness_goal DESC;
SELECT * FROM diet_impact_fitness_goals WHERE activity_level = 'High' AND weight > 70;
SELECT username, gender, height FROM diet_impact_fitness_goals WHERE age BETWEEN 25 AND 35;
SELECT username, age, weight FROM diet_impact_fitness_goals WHERE gender = 'Male' ORDER BY weight DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, diet_type, fitness_goal FROM diet_impact_fitness_goals WHERE age > 30 AND height < 170 ORDER BY age ASC;
SELECT * FROM diet_impact_fitness_goals WHERE activity_level = 'High' AND diet_type LIKE 'Vegetarian%' ORDER BY username ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, diet_type, activity_level FROM diet_impact_fitness_goals WHERE gender = 'Female' AND (age BETWEEN 25 AND 35 OR fitness_goal = 'Weight Loss') ORDER BY user_id DESC;
SELECT username, age, fitness_goal FROM diet_impact_fitness_goals WHERE activity_level = 'Moderate' OR (gender = 'Female' AND weight < 60) ORDER BY username, age;
SELECT * FROM user ORDER BY age ASC, weight DESC
SELECT user_id, username, fitness_goal FROM user WHERE age > 30
SELECT * FROM user WHERE fitness_goal = 'Lose Weight' OR fitness_goal = 'Build Muscle'
SELECT user_id, username, age FROM user WHERE age = 25 OR age = 30
SELECT username, age, weight FROM user WHERE age > 20 ORDER BY weight
SELECT * FROM user WHERE age > 30 AND fitness_goal = 'Weight Loss';
SELECT user_id, username, age FROM user ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT username, weight FROM user WHERE fitness_goal = 'Muscle Gain' ORDER BY weight ASC;
SELECT user.username, diet_log.calorie_intake FROM user JOIN diet_log ON user.user_id = diet_log.user_id WHERE diet_log.calorie_intake > 2000;
SELECT user.username, SUM(diet_log.exercise_duration) AS total_exercise_minutes FROM user JOIN diet_log ON user.user_id = diet_log.user_id GROUP BY user.username HAVING total_exercise_minutes > 60;
